hind her many tattoos.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.43828091517074e-16, \"text\": \"Sky Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the story\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1455}, {\"ngram\": \"her many tattoos\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a separate interview withActivate the Burners, Hodgkinson went into further detail about her Tokyo tattoo before explaining why she is never likely to get branded with the Olympic rings.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999898733652819, \"rank\": 1.0126737339663695e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999997535225102, \"rank\": 2.4119190581330537e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a separate interview\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"the Burners\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1530}, {\"ngram\": \"further detail\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This was my spontaneous tattoo on Oxford Street when I got back from Tokyo, so it says Tokyo,' she said.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\", \"score\": 0.990066275629917, \"rank\": 0.010032733886355685, \"text\": \"Oxford\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oxford\"}, {\"begin\": 1743, \"end\": 1748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999997535225102, \"rank\": 2.4119190581330537e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1761, \"end\": 1766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999997535225102, \"rank\": 2.4119190581330537e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Personally, no hate to anyone, I do not like the Olympic rings.\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like, I do like them but not on me.'\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What an incredible moment for Keely Hodgkinson \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b9#Paris2024#Olympics#BBCOlympicspic.twitter.com/CowXsXDFjF Asked if she was tempted to get the Olympic rings tattooed, Hodgkinson replied: 'No, I will not get them!\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 2098, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999898733652819, \"rank\": 1.0126737339663695e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"What an incredible moment\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"Keely Hodgkinson \\u00f0\\u009f\\u00a5\\u00b9#Paris2024#Olympics#BBCOlympicspic.twitter.com\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings tattooed\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I think they are really ugly.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, I just do not like them as a tattoo for me.\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I just do not think it would look right on me so I thought this [her Tokyo tattoo] was a bit more low-key.'\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999997535225102, \"rank\": 2.4119190581330537e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On her right arm, Hodgkinson has a tattoo paying tribute to her late grandparents and another nodding to her star sign, Pisces, which she got aged 18 and 'kind of regrets'.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2308, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999898733652819, \"rank\": 1.0126737339663695e-05, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2410, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fish\", \"score\": 0.9999999694978219, \"rank\": 3.050018088051753e-08, \"text\": \"Pisces\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fish\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fish\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her right arm\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"a tattoo paying tribute\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"her late grandparents\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2371}, {\"ngram\": \"another nodding\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"her star sign\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"'kind of regrets\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'These are for my grandparents who passed away,' she explained.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my grandparents\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is my star sign\\u2026 I kind of regret this one though\\u2026 I was 18.\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2595, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my star sign\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And then this one is matching with my best friend.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2615}, {\"ngram\": \"my best friend\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got all these when I was like 18 so do not judge me!\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After her remarkable win in the French capital, a near-speechless Hodgkinson said she simply 'could not believe' that she had achieved her life-long dream by claiming gold.\", \"from\": 2705, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9771408047703677, \"rank\": 0.018081391268710983, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2771, \"end\": 2781, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.9999